 tear the last couple years or so as the company has gone from the verge of bankruptcy to flying high at a $50 billion+ valuation. Up more than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679240705/image_1679240705.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741881-carvana-a-major-reason-you-should-avoid-this-overpriced-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4742034", "title": "KULR: A Penny Stock Connecting The Dots Between EVTOLs, Data Centers, Space Batteries, And SMRs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of blackjack in casino\" data-id=\"102284502\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5120px\" height=\"3413px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Duncan Nicholls and Simon Webb</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Lately, I\u2019ve been closely monitoring penny stocks, particularly those connected to the latest <em>hot</em> topics like eVTOLs, data centers, batteries, space, and SMRs. I must admit, I haven\u2019t come across any penny stock with as much exposure to all these</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/102284502/image_102284502.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742034-kulr-a-penny-stock-connecting-the-dots-between-evtols-data-centers-space-batteries-and-smrs", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 15:40:10"}, {"id": "4741971", "title": "Northern Star Acquires De Grey: A Near-Record Purchase Price For A Developer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Inside the giant Super Pit or Fimiston Open Pit, the largest open pit gold mine of Australia.\" data-id=\"2122119137\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2122119137/image_2122119137.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static